headline: Belcan Named Supplier of the Year by GE Aerospace
summary: Belcan, LLC (a Cognizant company), a global supplier of design, software, manufacturing, supply chain, information technology, and digital engineering solutions to the aerospace, defense, space, automotive, industrial, marine, and government services markets, today announced that it has been named Supplier of the Year by GE Aerospace.
